examples.en: Anger flooded him.
The sunlight flooded into the room.
The flood left them homeless.
The flood took many lives.
Heavy rains flooded the valley.
The village was cut off by floods.
Japanese cars have flooded the market.
The flood subsides.
We have been flooded with responses to our advertisement.
examples.ru: Мы получили поток откликов на наше объявление.

examples.en: The images flooded his mind.
examples.ru: Эти образы заполнили все его мысли.

examples.en: Our basement flooded during the heavy rains.
examples.ru: Наш подвал затопило во время ливней.

examples.en: The flood devastated the town.
The water has risen to flood level.
Light flooded into the room.
We've received a flood of mail.
The room was flooded with light.
The plain floods every spring.
The flood of refugees continued unabated.
A flood of cheap import has come into the shops.
examples.ru: Огромное количество дешёвого импорта наводнило магазины.

examples.en: The rivers are close to flooding.
The swollen river flooded the village
examples.ru: Река, вышедшая из берегов, затопила деревню.

examples.en: Refugees flooded into the camp.
The flood caused great hardship.
The flood inundated several cities.
The flood waters are slowly retreating.
The flood level stood at three feet above usual for several weeks.
examples.ru: В течение нескольких недель уровень воды держался на три фута выше обычного.

examples.en: Light flooded into the kitchen.
examples.ru: Свет ворвался в кухню. / Кухня залилась светом.

examples.en: Four people drowned in the flood.
examples.ru: Четыре человека утонули во время наводнения.

examples.en: A flood inundated the whole area.
The flood raced through the valley.
